  <p><strong>Brosseau L, Ann RL.</strong> <a href="https://blogs.cdc.gov/niosh-science-blog/2009/10/14/n95/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">N95 respirators and surgical masks</a>. NIOSH Science Blog. Oct 14, 2009</p>
<p><strong>Jones R, Brosseau L.</strong> <a href="https://insights.ovid.com/article/00043764-201505000-00004" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Aerosol transmission of infectious disease</a>. J Occup Environ Med 2015 May;57(5):501-8</p>
